  "contentHtml": "\n\n                    <!-- Display video article in news article for the custom next story -->\n                    \n                    <!-- Modifying the body placing embeds,promoslots,related etc.-->\n                                        <figure><img src=\"/images/default.jpg\" alt=\"\"></figure><p>Chandigarh: <a href=\"/tag/rj+corp+healthcare\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">RJ Corp Healthcare</a> has expanded its footprint to Chandigarh with the launch of Cocoon Hospital in the city.The healthcare company said, “The premium mother and child healthcare facility is dedicated to delivering integrated, technology-enabled and compassionate care for women, mothers, newborns and children.”The launch comes as Chandigarh emerges as a major hub for advanced medical services through both public and private sector investments, it added.</p><!-- PROMOSLOT_M --><p>\"Alongside the upcoming pipeline projects in Lucknow and Guwahati, this network expansion is poised to set new benchmarks in pregnancy care, neonatal medicine and paediatric healthcare for families across Chandigarh, Punjab, Haryana, Himachal Pradesh and the wider North India region,\" a press statement said.                    </p><!-- Category Most Read Placement -->\n                                                                    \n                                                                \n                                <ul>\n                                                                            <!-- <li>By <span>Online Bureau</span>,</li> -->\n                                    \n\n                                                                            <li>By\n                                                                                            <a>Online Bureau</a>\n\n                                                                                                                                                                                   